learning_outcomes.en:
A student who has passed the course is able to
* recognize and understand medical terms in the context;
* read and find the main idea of a text concerning his / her speciality;
* follow a lecture on his / her speciality 
* find and present relevant information to the colleague (using terms) and to the   patient in the form of a discussion or a presentation;
* deliver academic presentation on medical topics;
* write a summary of a special text;

learning_outcomes.et:
Kursuse läbinud üliõpilane
* suudab määratleda loetu peaideed;
* oskab tekstist leida vajalikku infot;
* oskab vahetada infot, vestelda kursuse põhiteemadel ning esitada ja põhjendada oma vaateid ning seisukohti;
* oskab loetu ja kuuldu põhjal märkmeid teha, olulist kokku võtta; 
* oskab kirjutada kirjeldavaid, analüüsivaid ja arutlevaid loovtöid;

description.et:
Eristav hindamine. Sõnavara ja grammatika teemast "Apteegis". 
Grade 'A': 100%-91% of the correct answers;
Grade 'B': 90%-81% of the correct answers;
Grade 'C':80%-71% of the correct answers;
Grade 'D': 70%-61% of the correct answers;
Grade 'E': 60%-51% of the correct answers;
Grade 'F':50%-0% of the correct answers;

